{"id":1733942,"retrievedAt":"2026-07-20T13:26:58.379Z","response":{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":null,"belongs_to_collection":null,"budget":0,"genres":[],"homepage":"","id":1733942,"imdb_id":null,"origin_country":["US"],"original_language":"en","original_title":"Nurlaila","overview":"# The Story of Imran  The life story of a young man named Imran, son of a wealthy family, who frequently quarrels with his stepfather, Khalid, because he disapproves of his father's attitude towards his mother, Aina, who is suffering from brain cancer. Imran, a young man who refuses to follow in his father's footsteps and wants to build his own life, is always hot-tempered when facing Khalid. The two of them often argue and never see eye to eye. In the midst of this turmoil, Aina often tries her best to improve the father-son relationship. Without Aina's knowledge, Khalid is having a secret affair with Sara, the secretary at their company. When Imran decides to leave home to clear his mind, he accidentally meets a village girl named Nurlaila. Laila is actually fleeing from Pak Tono, her father's associate and a chicken farm owner, who wants to sell her into prostitution. Imran saves Laila and gives her a place to stay. Laila feels indebted to this man.","popularity":0.0143,"poster_path":"/mxwt4Pcy1jnvPvjiMv40KisF59v.jpg","production_companies":[{"id":119726,"logo_path":null,"name":"Luqsar Kreatif Sdn Bhd","origin_country":""}],"production_countries":[],"release_date":"2022-01-01","revenue":0,"runtime":0,"softcore":false,"spoken_languages":[],"status":"Released","tagline":"","title":"Nurlaila","video":false,"vote_average":0,"vote_count":0,"alternative_titles":{"titles":[]},"credits":{"cast":[{"adult":false,"gender":1,"id":2146084,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Hanna Aqeela","original_name":"Hanna Aqeela","popularity":0.4555,"profile_path":"/ochtpIpHZwwP90d10r7oMOccaYU.jpg","cast_id":4,"character":"","credit_id":"6a5caf35fad6eee62d93dd24","order":0},{"adult":false,"gender":2,"id"